Package: CausalModel
Title: Causal Inference Estimators for Observational and Experimental Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zhaonan", "Qu", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "zhaonanq@stanford.edu"),
    person("CausalModel Contributors", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Implements causal inference estimators for observational studies,
    randomized experiments, and network interference settings. Provides OLS,
    IPW, AIPW, matching, and double machine learning estimators for
    observational data; difference-in-means, stratified, and ANCOVA estimators
    for experiments; and clustered IPW/AIPW estimators for interference
    settings. Based on Qu et al. (2021).
